OL,3,GGrampian
OL,4,
OL,5,CWednesday:FA dry and sunny start then
OL,6,Fcloud bubbling up through the morning
OL,7,Fwith showers developing. Some showers
OL,8,Fcould be heavy and thundery in the
OL,9,Fafternoon.
OL,10,
OL,11,COutlook for Thursday to Saturday:
OL,12,FCloudy with outbreaks of rain on
OL,13,FThursday. Mainly dry with sunny spells
OL,14,Fon Friday and Saturday and becoming
OL,15,Fwarmer.
